How to watch Chelsea v West Ham, live stream and TV channel
Chelsea v West Ham will be broadcast live on Sky Sports Football and Sky Sports Main Event. Streaming will also be available via Sky Sports+ and the Sky Sports app.

Chelsea v West Ham kick-off time, date and venue
Chelsea v West Ham will be played at Stamford Bridge and kick-off is at 20:00 (GMT) on Monday 3rd February, 2025.

Chelsea v West Ham stats and head-to-head record (H2H)
Chelsea hold the stronger head-to-head record in this fixture and have won the previous two encounters by an 8-0 aggregate score.

Enzo Maresca's men have won win in their previous seven league fixtures and both teams have scored in five of those clashes.

West Ham have four points from three games under Potter and came from behind to earn a 1-1 draw at Aston Villa last Sunday.
